<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>go at large • go big</xh5><p> <i>go at large—</i>be permitted to move freely about at will: The question is to decide whether it is safe to allow the prisoner to <u>go at large</u>.</p><p><i>go big</i>—(coll., also: go big time) 1. operate on a large scale: I really like to barbecue and we decided to <u>go big</u> as the sale price was great. 2. enjoy a great success: After winning both days down in Colombia, Donny decided to <u>go big</u> on the dance floor as well.</p> </entry>
